messages.message:
Hi team - some feedback from VRSF
"When evaluating my validations, the actual names of the validations are not displayed on the table view, instead they are just called rule 1, rule 2 etc which makes it really hard to track which rule is which. Especially since these rules are ordered alphabetically, which means that rule 10 comes before rule 2, which makes it even harder:"
Its actually better to at least provide the same name we show in the side editor panel cc: @Weiming Wu what do you think?

Yea we've discussed this so many times and kicked the can down the road. I'll do some exploration today since I'm waiting for other feature work and see how impactful it is.
(I'm hoping it's not too bad)
Yeah lets do a sync on this before we pick anything up but updated Leilas ticket
